Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,251)}A.niger：黑曲霉\N学名Aspergillus niger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an9\pos(854,292)}M.mucedo: 蜂毛霉菌 霉白霉菌\N学名Mucor mucedo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过怎么办好啊 美里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷静下来 好好想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:12:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,333)}Candida:白色念珠菌\N学名Candida albicans
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:12:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an9\pos(854,17)}C.tricoides：黑霉\N学名Cladosporium tricoides
