Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法想啦 方案和钱都用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,17)}R.javanicus:爪哇根霉\N学名Rhizopus javanicus
