Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an9\pos(854,17)}Geotrichum sp.：地霉属\N全称不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an9\pos(854,192)}A.niger：黑曲霉\N学名Aspergillus niger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少募集来的钱也得想法儿还掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是闹着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先把房间里有的东西拿去卖掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们二位是打算用那个酒做买卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划在春季学院祭典上开店的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是拜托我们就能便宜搞到酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从开店的那帮家伙手里收集了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是用集资的钱造的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情进展的顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积压的宿舍费也能还清了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下 正好想和泽木你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 能先通一下风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霉的数量超过玩笑的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 泽木 你能看到菌对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能用那个能力设法赚点钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}比如说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间里有没有新种类的菌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 不是新种类也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸菌之类的 能够卖上价钱的啥玩意儿有不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27\fad(0,100)}松茸菌：学名Tricholoma matsutake
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们招待到这里 原来是这样的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过遗憾的是 在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净是黑霉 青霉之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 青霉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青霉菌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青霉菌是从青霉之一 chrysogenum制成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽木你能够分辨菌对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也能纯粹的培养吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉一个这家伙 丢进培养皿就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,17)}P.chrysogenum\N学名Penicillium chrysogenum\N所谓的青霉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是看不到啦 不过大体就是那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯粹的P.chrysogenum的菌株的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能卖到实验室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺去和培养科交涉看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽木的能力要掩盖好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重点要主张能够制造百分百纯净的这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这么说来我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一直收集青霉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就当作相识也是某种缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会给你赚头的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赚头是指…钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「青霉这种东西 我家多得是能卖」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺被培养的教授给说了
 Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我开窗了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 川滨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你养的大锹卖掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27\fad(0,100)}大锹：学名Dorcus hopei 一种珍贵甲虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没招儿啊 不想办法不成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你把我给你的蚕的幼虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚕丝剥下来拿去卖呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(0,100)}木盒上的字：蚕 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是你给我的蚕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果只是蛾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且都死光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要咋办啊 丫的 你倒是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦 知道了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冬虫夏草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬虫夏草？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说中国的那个长生不老的秘药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都死了被腐败菌吞噬着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,312)}腐败菌：能够腐败有机物的菌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,104)}C.sinensis：冬虫夏草菌\N学名Cordyceps sinensis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有一只被冬虫夏草菌包围着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来倒是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你是怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 记得大桥那里的关口阿姨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人经常邮购这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级小的盒子 好像说是2万块什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2万！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(0,100)}囧 当然是日元啦 大概RMB1300
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然的因为很难找到 貌似很贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个培养下 不能卖到中药店什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽木 拜托啦 帮俺们一把
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是可以啦 这点小事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬虫夏草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}真的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能解决了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要庆祝庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽木 这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 从来没有人因为我能看到菌这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人依赖 还真是件愉快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}万岁 万岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(0,100)}囧 这俩人胳膊不酸么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽木君的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了他们俩的手上 也不过是赚钱的工具么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样我也有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,351)\fs20\fr17\fad(200,0)}{\bord0\shad0\1c&H000000&}估\N价\N单\N在\N内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生要赔偿这个金额的话应该很困难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}为了欢迎你俩入学 为了我们的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(443,167)}{\fs20\bord0\shad0\1c&H000000&}{\fad(0,1000)}蚕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长谷川同学今天已经要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我还有想要做的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs27}告知：\N\N{\fs20}以下的人请于本日10点 到旧农学部西栋树研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs20}一年 泽木直保 结城萤\N二年川滨拓马 美里熏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs20}不来你们就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不过明天你要空出时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已经漆黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去树老师那里一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书包落在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正大家都还在睡 趁现在去了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有像长谷川小姐和树老师那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要考验我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的话要么躲远要么怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会觉得不快的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 泽木君他好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏说看到了 真是恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽木家的直保 真是有点与众不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说很多怪话企图引起注意 也是小孩子常做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么能看到菌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不想吃 就直接说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说谎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 直保  快吃饭打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 直保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住 要飞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这帮家伙久违地玩玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色的 到这边集合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄色的霉就把饭团当作托盘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 这不是泽木的另一半吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你还在学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在刚才惹事的那两个学长的宿舍里来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:18:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 书包忘在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这事啊 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很辛苦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后 你打算怎样和泽木相处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎样…我们之间没有任何问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况是酒厂和种曲店的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计会成为毕生之交…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来给你个善意的忠告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子能看到菌的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我们的一套透射电子显微镜相当 这么想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有3亿元的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(0,100)}3亿日元 大概人民币2000万
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3亿元么…怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子的能力被人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企图利用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不会仅仅是树老师和胡子和胖子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菌剧场 2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫chrysogenum 俗称青霉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(110,100)}{\1c&H9EA35B&}chrysogenum
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(110,416)}{\1c&H9EA35B&}青 霉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢湿气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是tricoides
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\1c&HA68891&}{\pos(110,70)}tricoides
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在浴室的地砖缝隙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是变黑的地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也被叫做黑霉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\1c&HA68891&}{\pos(110,70)}黑 霉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 好啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真是热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,100)}{\1c&Hc67d04&}alternata
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,200)}{\1c&Hc67d04&}链格孢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是alternata 俗称链格孢霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好保养的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是隐形眼镜的洗涤液 也会酿掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空调的内部也隐藏着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是霉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你丫个霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间 到处都是霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个棒房间
